text: Paula Törnqvist (born 24 February 1964) is a Swedish equestrian. She competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Sweden Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Gothenburg
